

entity layer
_: empty (no entity)
1: the first creature (rat)
2: the second creature (turtle)
3: the third creature (bird)
4: the fourth creature (frog)
G: goal zone
R: boulder

terrain layer
_: ground
W: water (for frog)
X: wall
C: chasm (for bird)
T: tunnel (for rat)


B: button
S: switch
H: bridge


